            </div>
            <div class="cell small-12 medium-6">
                <p>The School of Health Professions prepares outstanding healthcare professionals and leaders in the allied health fields. These providers may be the first responders in medical emergencies, the discerning eyes in the lab, or the physical therapists making a home visit.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cell small-12 medium-6">
                <p>UT Health provides degrees in seven allied fields: Emergency Health Sciences, Medical Laboratory Sciences, Occupational Therapy, Physical Therapy, Physician Assistant Studies, Respiratory Care, Medical Sciences and Imaging Sciences and Speech-Language Pathology.</p>
